how do you get honey in escape from bug island for the wii i find a tree covered in honey with the ants crawling on it eating the honey all the other trees have no honey but have the ants i need the honey to preoccupy the ants so they don't blow up and hurt me how do i get the honey for the other trees in stage head west and go across bridge gorilla won't follow on bridge head north east making sure to kill anything necessary head east across bridge avoiding the flying fish head north curving towards the left unless you have killed the gorilla going right just isn't worth it at the broken bridge throw rocks at the log stuck in the water to dislodge it keep following the path extremely linear here after the next bridge with more flying fish look towards the tree tops there's a steel pipe waiting to be knocked down after the steel pipe segment is another broken bridge do the same thing as before keep heading west until you curve south in one of the boxes is the safe key head north and go into the shack use the safe key and get the honey head east to finish the level more help http www gamefaqs com console wii file Diving Mario Professional wrestling holds Poker jargon Professional wrestling match types Pikmin Jet Force Gemini Diseases of the honeybee Piccolo Junior Saga Sonic the Hedgehog 2 American Black Bear Spidey Super Stories Beehive (beekeeping) RuneScape quests Ant RuneScape skills GameFAQs Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Honeybee Naruto jutsu RuneScape Random Events Happy Tree Friends Escape from New York Mario series enemies Super Mario Land 2: 6 Golden Coins Professional wrestling slang Independent Subway System Tag Elis Prefecture The Inside Baseball Civil engineering and infrastructure repair in New Orleans after Hurricane Katrina Bridge The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie Labor Day Hurricane of 1935 Bee Professional wrestling throws Aerial (dance move) Ice hockey Conker's Bad Fur Day Thor (Marvel Comics) Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Radiohead Sup